RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION, RTGS_PRODUCT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR B, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD C WHERE A.MODULE = 'OL' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND B.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT K, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = K.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE) ORDER BY A.PRODUCT_CODE

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO, B.SHORT_NAME,B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CUSTOMERS A, STTM_CORE_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO
SELECT EXTERNAL_VALUE FROM OLTMS_TRANSLATION WHERE TRANSLATION_TYPE = 'AGENT_CIF' AND SOURCE_CODE = 'STP'

SELECT VW.CCY_CODE, CCY.CCY_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CURRENCIES VW, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN CCY WHERE VW.CCY_CODE = CCY.CCY_CODE AND VW.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND CCY.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND CCY.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY VW.CCY_CODE
SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_CCY, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE (BRANCH_CODE IS NOT NULL OR AC_OR_GL = 'G') AND GL_ACLASS_TYPE <> '5' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, ?) = NVL(?, '*') AND (A.AC_OR_GL = 'G' OR (A.AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE A.AC_GL_NO = X.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?))) ORDER BY DECODE(NVL(AC_GL_CCY, '*'), ?, 1, 2), DECODE(NVL(CUST_NO, '*'), ?, 1, 2), AC_GL_NO, BRANCH_CODE

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY AGENT, CURRENCY FROM OLTMS_INSTR WHERE DECODE(COUNTERPARTY, 'ALL', NVL(?, ?), COUNTERPARTY) = NVL(?, ?) AND DECODE(BRANCH, 'ALL', ?, BRANCH) = ? AND DECODE(MODULE, 'AL', 'OL', MODULE) = 'OL' AND DECODE(PRODUCT_CODE, 'ALL', ?, PRODUCT_CODE) = ? AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ? UNION ALL SELECT 1 FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)
SELECT A.STATUS, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER A, OLTMS_CONTRACT_STATUSES B WHERE A.PRODUCT = ? AND A.STATUS = B.STATUS_CODE AND B.STATUS_TYPE = 'C' ORDER BY A.STATUS_SEQUENCE
SELECT DAY,VALUE FROM OLVW_STATEMENT_DAY WHERE INDICATOR = DECODE(?, 'A','A', 'Q','A', 'S','A','M','D', 'F','F', 'W','F', 'D','D')ORDER BY VALUE

SELECT VW.CCY_CODE, CCY.CCY_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CURRENCIES VW, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN CCY WHERE VW.CCY_CODE = CCY.CCY_CODE AND VW.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND CCY.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND CCY.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY VW.CCY_CODE
SELECT ADMIN_ID, ADMIN_NAME FROM OLTM_ADMINISTRATOR WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
SELECT INDUSTRY_CODE,INDUSTRY_DESC FROM OLTMS_INDUSTRY WHERE AUTH_STAT='A'AND RECORD_STAT='O'

SELECT FUNDING_REF_NO, DESCRIPTION, FUNDING_AMOUNT, EXTERNAL_REF_NO FROM OLTMS_POOL_FUNDING_MASTER WHERE BRANCH_CODE = ? AND FUNDING_CCY =? AND FUNDING_TYPE = 'P' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT FUNDING_REF_NO, DESCRIPTION, FUNDING_AMOUNT, EXTERNAL_REF_NO FROM OLTMS_POOL_FUNDING_MASTER WHERE BRANCH_CODE =? AND FUNDING_CCY = ? AND FUNDING_TYPE = 'M' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND COUNTERPARTY = ?

SELECT DISTINCT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLLOVER B, OLTBS_CONTRACT C, OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE D WHERE A.BRANCH = ? AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = C.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = D.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND C.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND B.ROLL_INST_STATUS <> 'C' AND A.PRODUCT = ? AND A.COUNTERPARTY = ? AND A.CURRENCY = ? AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE L WHERE L.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND L.DUE_DATE = (SELECT MAX(DUE_DATE) FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE_CS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = L.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND COMPONENT = 'PRINCIPAL' AND NVL(MSG_EVENT_SEQ_NO, 0) > 0) AND A.MATURITY_DATE = ?

SELECT A.FUND_ID, A.FUND_DESCRIPTION, A.FUND_REFERENCE_NO FROM AMTMS_FUND_MASTER A WHERE A.BRANCH_CODE = ? AND A.VERSION_NO = (SELECT B.LATEST_VERSION_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT B WHERE B.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.FUND_REFERENCE_NO AND B.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND B.AUTH_STATUS = 'A') ORDER BY A.FUND_ID
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO LINKED_TO_REF, A.BRANCH LINKED_TO_BRANCH, B.CURRENCY LINKED_TO_CURRENCY, B.FACILITY_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTB_CONTRACT_BORROWERS D WHERE A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND B.VALUE_DATE <= ? AND NVL(B.MATURITY_DATE, '31-DEC-75') >= NVL(?, '31-DEC-75') AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = D.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND D.CUSTOMER_NO = ? AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_EVENT_LOG C WHERE C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND NVL(AUTH_STATUS, 'U') = 'A') UNION SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO LINKED_TO_REF, A.BRANCH LINKED_TO_BRANCH, B.CURRENCY LINKED_TO_CURRENCY, B.FACILITY_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTBS_BORR_PROD_LIMIT C WHERE A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'C' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND B.VALUE_DATE <= ? AND NVL(B.MATURITY_DATE, '31-DEC-75') >= NVL(?, '31-DEC-75') AND C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND (C.LOAN_PRODUCT = 'ALL' OR C.LOAN_PRODUCT = ?) AND (C.CCY_CODE = 'ALL' OR C.CCY_CODE = ?) AND C.BORROWER = ? ORDER BY LINKED_TO_REF

SELECT DISTINCT B.RATE_CODE, B.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE B WHERE B.BRANCH_CODE = ? AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='S' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'

SELECT COMPONENT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_DFLT_SCHEDULES WHERE PRODUCT = ? UNION SELECT 'INSTALMENT' FROM OLTM_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND ALLOW_INSTALMENT = 'Y' UNION SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT CS, OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER LD WHERE CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LD.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CS.LATEST_VERSION_NO = LD.VERSION_NO AND NVL(LD.AGENCY_CONTRACT, 'N') = 'Y') UNION SELECT CF.COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE CF, LFTM_PRODUCT_FEE FE, OLTB_CONTRACT CS, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER LD WHERE CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CF.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(CF1.EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE CF1 WHERE CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CF1.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CF.COMPONENT = CF1.COMPONENT) AND FE.COMPONENT = CF.COMPONENT AND LD.CONTRACT_REF_NO = CS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CS.LATEST_VERSION_NO = LD.VERSION_NO AND sypks_utils.get_product(CF.CONTRACT_REF_NO) = FE.PRODUCT_CODE AND NVL(LD.AGENCY_CONTRACT, 'N') = 'N' AND FE. BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG <> 'USERINPUT' UNION SELECT component FROM lftms_product_iccf WHERE product = ? AND basis_amount_category = 'D' MINUS SELECT 'PRINCIPAL' FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND VERSION_NO = ? AND NVL(ROLLING_LOAN, 'N') = 'Y' AND MATURITY_TYPE = 'C' MINUS SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND NVL(RETAIN_MAIN_COMP_PROP, 'N') = 'Y'

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, B.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_FLOATING_RATE A, CFTMS_RATE_CODE B WHERE A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND A.CCY_CODE = ? AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY A.RATE_CODE

select bcrefno,BILL_CCY,BILL_DUE_AMOUNT,BILL_AMT_AVAIL from oltb_bill_details where product_type = 'E' and linktoloan = 'Y' and lc_flag = 'N' and maturity_date > global.application_date and bill_due_amount > 0

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.CONTRACT_REF_NO = OLTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTLS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.BRANCH = OLTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTLS.BRANCH_CODE AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.VERSION_NO = OLTBS_ACC_COLL_LINK_DTLS.VERSION_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM STTM_CORE_BRANCH WHERE AUTH_STAT='A' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' ORDER BY BRANCH_CODE
select ccy_code, ccy_name from CYTMS_CCY_DEFN where auth_stat = 'A' AND record_stat = 'O' ORDER BY CCY_CODE

SELECT * FROM((SELECT 'A' default_liab,l.Line_Code || l.Line_Serial Linkage_Ref_No, 'F' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = l.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, l.Brn Branch, l.Line_Currency Currency, l.Description, l.Line_Expiry_Date Expiry_Date, l.facility_type facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Facility l, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE l.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.RECORD_STAT='O' AND Cust.AUTH_STAT='A' AND l.Liab_Id = Cust.Liab_Id AND l.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND l.Availability_Flag = 'Y' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY' AND Nvl('LIABCIF', ?) = 'LIABCIF' AND Nvl('CNPTY', ?) = 'CNPTY' AND Nvl('PRDCD', ?) = 'PRDCD' AND Nvl('BRN', ?) = 'BRN' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY') UNION (SELECT 'A' default_liab ,Pp.Pool_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'P' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = Pp.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, Pp.Branch_Code Branch, Pool_Ccy Currency, Pp.Pool_Description, NULL Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Pool Pp, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Pp.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Liab_Id = Pp.Liab_Id AND Cust.RECORD_STAT='O' AND Cust.AUTH_STAT='A' AND Pp.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'A' default_liab,c.Collateral_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'T' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = c.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Branch_Code Branch, c.Collateral_Currency Currency, c.Collateral_Description, c.End_Date Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Collat c, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Cust.Liab_Id = c.Liab_Id AND c.Available = 'Y' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.RECORD_STAT='O' AND Cust.AUTH_STAT='A' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y')) WHERE Customer_No = Nvl(?, ?) AND Linkage_Type = ? AND (('A'= ?) OR ('S'= ? AND Liab_No = ?) OR Default_Liab = ?)
SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO,A.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER A WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO
SELECT LIAB_NO, DESCRIPTION, CURRENCY, EXPIRY_DATE FROM OLTB_CUSTOMER_LINES WHERE BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND CUSTOMER_ID = Nvl(?, ?)

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO LINKED_TO_REF, A.BRANCH LINKED_TO_BRANCH, B.CURRENCY LINKED_TO_CURRENCY,B.FACILITY_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_TYPE = ? AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND B.VALUE_DATE <= ? AND NVL(B.MATURITY_DATE, '31-DEC-75') >= NVL(?, '31-DEC-75') AND A.COUNTERPARTY = ? ORDER BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO
SELECT a.BCREFNO, a.BILL_CCY, a.BILL_DUE_AMT, (a.BILL_AMT-a.BILL_DUE_AMT) BILL_AVL_AMT, a.VALUE_DATE, a.MATURITY_DATE FROM BCTB_CONTRACT_MASTER a WHERE LINKED_TO_LOAN = 'Y'

SELECT TREASURY_SOURCE,SOURCE_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_TREASURY_SOURCE A,OLTMS_BRN_TREAS_PARAMS B WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.TREASURY_TYPE = B.BRANCH_TREASURY_TYPE AND B.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH
SELECT FIN_CENTRE,FIN_CENTRE_DESC FROM OLTM_FIN_CENTRE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
SELECT distinct A.counterparty,A.cust_name FROM OLVW_CONTRACT_SUMMARY A WHERE A.auth_status = 'A' AND A.contract_status = 'A' ORDER BY A.counterparty

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION, RTGS_PRODUCT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT A, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR B, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD C WHERE A.MODULE = 'OL' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND B.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND A.PRODUCT_CODE = C.PRODUCT AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT K, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS S WHERE S.USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = K.PRODUCT_CODE AND S.PRODUCT_CODE = B.PRODUCT_CODE) ORDER BY A.PRODUCT_CODE
